00:27:09,730 --> 00:27:11,600
<font color="yellow">Seol Ki Chan barusan datang kemari.</font>

461
00:27:14,330 --> 00:27:17,030
<font color="yellow">Baik. Akan kuselidiki itu sendiri.</font>

462
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:22,400
<font color="yellow">Dal Hee.</font>

463
00:27:23,660 --> 00:27:25,760
<font color="yellow">Kamu berulah lagi.</font>

464
00:27:32,230 --> 00:27:33,960
<font color="yellow">Kamu sudah mau berangkat kerja?</font>

465
00:27:37,360 --> 00:27:39,060
<font color="yellow">Aku penasaran akan satu hal.</font>

466
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:43,030
