497
00:29:20,500 --> 00:29:21,560
<font color="yellow">Dasar kamu...</font>

498
00:29:21,560 --> 00:29:23,960
<font color="yellow">Apa yang kamu bicarakan?</font>

499
00:29:23,960 --> 00:29:26,030
<font color="yellow">Ini tidak cukup jika kamu memikirkan</font>

