00:29:27,730 --> 00:29:31,130
<font color="yellow">Kalian berdua seharusnya dianggap sebagai perwujudan Buddha.</font>

502
00:29:36,430 --> 00:29:37,530
<font color="yellow">Aku pulang.</font>

503
00:29:39,100 --> 00:29:43,400
<font color="yellow">Selamat pagi.</font>

504
00:29:43,530 --> 00:29:44,760
<font color="yellow">Ki Chan, kita harus bicara.</font>

505
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:46,630
<font color="yellow">Suruh Ha Ri masuk juga.</font>

506
00:29:46,630 --> 00:29:48,530
<font color="yellow">Nikmatilah sarapan kalian berdua.</font>

507
00:29:54,300 --> 00:29:56,330
<font color="yellow">Kamu akan membiarkan Hong Si tinggal di sini sampai kapan?</font>

508
00:29:56,700 --> 00:29:58,830
<font color="yellow">Aku bahkan terlalu risi untuk tinggal di rumah sendiri.</font>

509
00:29:58,930 --> 00:30:00,130
<font color="yellow">Ibu rasa</font>

