00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:18,760
<font color="yellow">Pusat kesejahteraan?</font>

516
00:30:19,930 --> 00:30:21,460
<font color="yellow">Soal itu...</font>

517
00:30:21,460 --> 00:30:25,260
<font color="yellow">Sudah kubilang, Nona Kang Ha Ri bisa dituntut secara hukum.</font>

518
00:30:25,830 --> 00:30:28,100
<font color="yellow">Kirim dia ke pusat kesejahteraan sekarang juga</font>

