00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:37,000
<font color="yellow">Apa? Siapa dia?</font>

541
00:31:37,900 --> 00:31:39,000
<font color="yellow">Dal Hee.</font>

542
00:31:40,360 --> 00:31:41,460
<font color="yellow">Kamu yakin?</font>

543
00:31:42,030 --> 00:31:43,600
<font color="yellow">Pacarmu, Yang Dal Hee,</font>

