552
00:32:06,100 --> 00:32:07,530
<font color="yellow">Mari kita tunggu.</font>

553
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,660
<font color="yellow">Anda ingin bertemu denganku?</font>

554
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:21,030
